name: CUSTOM JC JUMPER
description:
Custom Jumper.
 
Email me with your idea & images and we can work together under my aesthetic to make you the PERF jumper.

All jumpers start with a deposit of 30, and suitable postage. (which you will pay for if you select this option) 

After you have paid via paypal: email your images, size of the jumper (S-XXL) and ideas to jade.clark1@btinternet.com. When your design has been seen and discussed, we will be able to give you a quote on how much your order will be and the time it will take via email.


** If you are unsure or have any questions before you pay your deposit, don't hesitate to email Jade on jade.clark1@btinternet.com

Thank you,
Jade
